                <section class="policy-section">
                    <h2>10. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
                    <p>TAUCHOPORTAL IS PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. SPECIFICALLY, WE DISCLAIM:</p>
                    <ul>
