                <section class="policy-section">
                    <h2>11. Indemnification</h2>
                    <p>You agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless TauchoPortal, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any claims, damages, losses, and expenses (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising from or related to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your use of the Service</li>
